/// <para>If target is afflicted with Kuzushi, deals damage equal to 100% of their maximum HP.</para>
/// <para>Ignores the effects of Guard when dealing damage.</para>
/// <para>The additional effect of Kuzushi cannot be applied to players riding machina and non-player combatants.</para>
